project_descr: Project is to support ministry of Local Government to implement District Development Programme, phase 3 (DDP3)

outputs.output_descr: 1. Finalize Local Economic Business Assessment for DDP3 pilot districts 2. National Level capacity for enhancement of Local Economic Development created.

District Development Programme III (DDP III) aims to contribute to the promotion of sustainable and equitable growth in the economy of target districts and to contribute to the alleviation of poverty and the achievement of the MDGs and through replication, achieve a similar outcome nation wide
